author: Soo Kim
title: China Coronavirus Cases Could Have Been Four Times Higher Than Officially Reported in February, Study Shows
description: Doubts over the accuracy of the virus figures officially reported by China's health commission have been raised for weeks.
content: The novel coronavirus in China was reported by Chinese authorities to have infected around 55,500 people by February 20. However, the total number of infections may have been four times as muchcloser to 232,000according to a research report by the School of P… [+7243 chars]
